<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1353] implement reusable token streams for all Solr tokenizers / token filters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1353</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The new lucene token architecture causes bad indexing performance if you don&apos;t happen to use reusable token streams.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12432631">SOLR-1353</key>
            <summary>implement reusable token streams for all Solr tokenizers / token filters</summary>
